  • Comprehensive Health Indicators Monitoring: Stay on top of your health with the blood pressure watch, which provides 24/7 monitoring of your heart rate, blood pressure. With real-time health data available directly on your fitness tracker, The accompanying app stores detailed health records, allowing you to analyze trends and keep your health in check and make improvements for a healthier lifestyle.
  • Intelligent Sleep Monitoring & Analysis: Improve your sleep quality with the Smart Watch’s intelligent sleep monitoring features. It tracks your sleep patterns, including light , awake and deep sleep stages, and provides you with detailed graphs and charts to help you better understand your sleep cycles. You can view your sleep data on a daily, weekly, or monthly basis through the FitCloudPro app, allowing you to identify patterns and adjust your habits for a more restful night.
  • Multi-Sport Modes & Activity Tracking: Whether you're running, cycling, or working out in the gym, the Smart Fitness Tracker supports 112 sports modes to track your performance. It functions as an accurate pedometer, measuring your steps, distance and calories burned in real-time. With the ability to set personalized exercise goals through the app, you can stay motivated and push achieve your health goals.
  • Real-Time Notifications for Calls & Messages: With the fitness watch, you can stay connected without constantly reaching for your phone. The watch delivers real-time notifications for incoming calls(Can't answer your phone), text messages, and app alerts (including Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram, and Messenger). Stay informed during workouts, meetings, or everyday tasks without missing important updates.
  • All-in-One Smart Assistant: This slim fitness tracking watch offers practical features like sedentary reminders, Drinking water reminder, menstrual cycle tracking, weather updates, and remote photo capture. It also includes a "Find Your Phone" function and customizable alarms to help you stay on top of your daily schedule.
  • Stylish and Durable Design: With a 1.57" HD touch screen and over 148 customizable watch faces, the watch allows you to personalize your style. It also features an IP68 waterproof rating, making it safe to wear in the rain or shine (though not suitable for diving or surfing).
  • Compatibility: The MorePro Fitness Tracker is compatible with Android 6.0 and iOS 10 and above smartphones with Bluetooth LE 5.2, but is not compatible with PCs, iPads or tablets. It can be used for 7-10 days on a single full charge. (Varies with usage and other factors)

Product description

Elevate Your Everyday - Transform Your Life with MorePro Air 2

The MorePro Fitness Tracker tracks your heart rate, blood pressure, and blood oxy-gen levels with ease. Stay on top of your health with heart rate alerts, blood pressure monitoring, and smart sleep tracking to help you rest and recharge for the day ahead. Perfect for a healthier lifestyle!

Scientific sleep tracking

Enhance your sleep with the MorePro AIR 2 fitness tracker! Offers precise, reliable data on deep/light sleep, wake times, and naps. Empowers you to improve sleep quality for tranquil nights and energetic days. Experience easy joy and better health!

Fitness Tracking & Smart Message Notification

100+ Sports Modes Tracking

The Air 2 activity tracker supports over 100 sports modes. Additionally, it now automatically recognizes five activities: walking, running, cycling, elliptical training, and rowing, thanks to the latest tech upgrade. It offers precise, activity-specific data to enhance your performance tracking.

Message Alerts on the MorePro Smart Watch

Stay connected with the MorePro Smartwatch! Sync it with your smartphone to receive notifications for calls, texts, emails, and app alerts. You can easily manage which apps trigger alerts directly from the app. Never miss an important message even while you’re on the go!

Menstrual tracking &15 days long standby time

Menstrual tracking: Empower Your Health Journey

Easily monitor your menstrual cycle with the Air2 Smart Fitness Tracker. Once you’ve set it up in the app for the first time, Air2 keeps you ahead of your cycle with reminders and logs for your period and ovulation. Stay balanced and keep your life in order with the help of Air2.

1-hour charge, 15-day power

Charge up your Air 2 fitness tracker in just 1 hour! Say goodbye to the hassle of constant recharging and enjoy an incredible 15-day battery life. Seamlessly monitor your fitness, sleep, and health, maintaining peak performance for goal-focused freedom and a vibrant life.

Ergonomic & Aesthetic Air 2 Fitness Watch

Stylish, ergonomic design for ultimate comfort and aesthetics meticulously crafted for a perfect fit

Stay Hydrated, Stay Energetic

Stay hydrated with personalized reminders to drink water throughout the day, keeping you energized.

Choice of Health, Gift of Love

Health guardian for loved ones: monitors heart rate, sleep, and style. Your love in every data beat.

              What’s Inside?

              Fitness Tracker: Embrace a positive and effortless lifestyle, starting with Air 2.

              Replacement Nylon Straps: Enjoy the complimentary durable and comfortable nylon straps that give your activity tracker a fresh, stylish look.

              Charging Cable: USB-designed for quick and easy charging of your device.

              Owner’s Manual: Our clear, user-friendly manual guides you through setup and feature exploration.

              Universal Size - Adjustable Strap to Fit All Wrist Sizes

              Experience ultimate comfort with Air 2 smart watch, featuring an adjustable strap designed for wrists measuring 5.71-8.86 inches. Its discreet design seamlessly blends practicality with style, ensuring a fashionable and enjoyable wear every time. Crafted from premium materials, it offers a soft touch and exceptional durability, making it the perfect companion for all your moments. Don’t wait, elevate your daily lifestyle with this essential accessory now!

              FitCloudPro App - Easy Download and Pairing Guide

              Download the ‘FitCloudPro’ app for free from the app store or scan the QR code on the packaging to download directly. Connect your fitness tracker through the app to access more features, enjoy comprehensive data recording, and personalize your experience. Track your workouts, monitor your health metrics, and discover over 100 watch faces waiting for you!
